---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Donate
description: "Support The Fullest Project and help us connect more families to disability resources."
permalink: /donate/
---

<section class="py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Support Our Mission</h1>
    <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
      The Fullest Project is building a free, comprehensive resource hub for families navigating disability. Your donation helps us maintain and expand our directory, create educational content, and keep everything accessible to everyone.
    </p>

    <!-- Every.org Donate Button -->
    <div class="card p-8 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Make a Donation</h2>
      <p class="mb-6" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        Donations are processed securely through Every.org. You can make a one-time gift or set up a recurring donation.
      </p>
      <div id="every-org-widget" class="mb-6">
        <!-- Replace YOUR_EVERY_ORG_SLUG below with your actual Every.org nonprofit slug -->
        <!-- To set up: visit https://www.every.org/nonprofits and register your organization -->
        <a href="https://www.every.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary no-underline text-lg px-8 py-4 inline-block">
          Donate via Every.org
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        Once your Every.org nonprofit profile is set up, we'll embed the donation widget directly on this page.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- What Donations Support -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F4DA;</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Resource Research</h3>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Fund the research and verification of disability resources across all 50 states.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F4BB;</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Website & Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Keep the website running, ad-free, and accessible to all families who need it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">&#x1F91D;</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Community Programs</h3>
        <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">Support community events, content creation, and caregiver support initiatives.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Other Ways to Help -->
    <div class="card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Other Ways to Help</h2>
      <ul class="text-left space-y-3 max-w-lg mx-auto" style="color: var(--color-text-light);">
        <li><a href="/submit-resource/" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Submit a resource</a> you know about to help grow our directory</li>
        <li><a href="/quick-submit/" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Install our bookmarklet</a> and submit resources as you browse</li>
        <li>Share The Fullest Project with friends, therapists, teachers, and support groups</li>
        <li><a href="/contact/" style="color: var(--color-secondary);">Contact us</a> about partnership or volunteer opportunities</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
